snippet.title: Dune: Spice Wars - Official 1.0 Release Window Announcement Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Dune: Spice Wars' version 1.0 will be available in September 2023. Watch the latest trailer for another look at gameplay and learn more about the story of this 4X real-time strategy game.
